      "source": [
        "### Discovery B — the CTR cliff by position\n",
        "Click-through rate is not flat: it collapses as you move down the results."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 6,
      "id": "5f223e16",
      "metadata": {
